main event: Multiple witnesses reported observing a bright luminous disc-shaped object over Tinker Air Force Base in Oklahoma, with durations of observation ranging from 5 to 30 minutes.
interesting points: The object was described as metallic and reflective, observed at altitudes between 1,000 to 50,000 feet,The object made no sound during the observation period,Several witnesses reported that the object hovered, changed direction, and accelerated at high speeds,No physical evidence or identification of the object was obtained,The sightings coincided with clear weather conditions and multiple reports from different individuals.
witness description: Civilian guards and control tower operators at Tinker AFB
